<H1>Perforce / ClearCase Performance - a Comparison</H1>
<H2>Copyright Parrus Technologies =95 10 Feb 2006</H2></DIV></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dpresentation>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>A Comparison of Perforce and ClearCase Performance issues</H1>
<H3>Steven R. Kroeker</H3>
<H4><A href=3D"http://www.parrus.com/">Parrus =
Technologies</A></H4></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Presentation Overview</H1>
<P>
<UL>
  <LI>An approach to perfomance analysis=20
  <LI>A review of Perforce and ClearCase models=20
  <LI>Selected operations from the Software Development Life Cycle=20
  <LI>Question and Answer Discussion </LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Performance Analysis Approach</H1>
<H4>Repeated Identification and Addressing the current Performance=20
Bottleneck.</H4>
<UL class=3Dincremental>
  <LI>Identify current Performance Bottleneck=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Need to determine the measurement points based on architecture =
model=20
    </LI></UL>
  <LI>Address Performance Bottleneck, directly or indirectly=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Sometimes "correct" fix is not available or too costly =
</LI></UL>
  <LI>Repeat until Performance is acceptable </LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Perforce Performance Model</H1>
<DIV style=3D"TEXT-ALIGN: center"><IMG title=3D"Perforce Model" alt=3D"" =

src=3D"http://scm.parrus-it.com/PPT/pix/p4model.jpg"> </DIV></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>ClearCase Performance Model</H1>
<DIV style=3D"TEXT-ALIGN: center"><IMG title=3D"ClearCase Model" =
alt=3D""=20
src=3D"http://scm.parrus-it.com/PPT/pix/CCover.jpg"> </DIV></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Selected operations from SDLC</H1>
<TABLE width=3D"100%" border=3D2>
  <TBODY>
  <TR>
    <TH>Perforce</TH>
    <TH>ClearCase</TH></TR>
  <TR>
    <TD>P4 client</TD>
    <TD>ct mkview dynamic or Join Project snapshot</TD></TR>
  <TR>
    <TD>P4 sync</TD>
    <TD>ct update and ct rebase</TD></TD>
  <TR>
    <TD>Checkout</TD>
    <TD>Checkout</TD></TD>
  <TR>
    <TD>-</TD>
    <TD>Checkin</TD></TD>
  <TR>
    <TD>Merge</TD>
    <TD>Merge</TD></TD>
  <TR>
    <TD>P4 submit</TD>
    <TD>ct deliver</TD></TD>
  <TR>
    <TD>Build</TD>
    <TD>Build</TD></TD>
  <TR>
    <TD>Label</TD>
    <TD>Label</TD></TD>
  <TR>
    <TD colSpan=3D2>Differences in an the approach to Branch =
operation</TD></TD>
  <TR>
    <TD>Proxy</TD>
    <TD>MultiSite</TD></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Workspace Setup</H1>
<UL>
  <LI>Perforce - client, sync=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Small I/O for Client Spec=20
    <LI>DB "Walk" and transfer of specified version contents to =
workspace=20
  </LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase Dynamic - mkview, setcs=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Small VOB I/O to record view=20
    <LI>Moderate I/O to setup View DB and structure </LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase Snapshot - mkview, setcs=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Small VOB I/O to record view=20
    <LI>Process of ConfigSpec Load rules against current View DB and VOB =
DB with=20
    transfer of versions to View workspace </LI></UL></LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Synchronize WorkSpace / Repository</H1>
<UL>
  <LI>Perforce - sync=20
  <UL>
    <LI>"Walk" the server DB for specified files, check to see if =
updated since=20
    last sync, transfer files to workspace if DB indicates file updated=20
    <LI>Can specify portion of workspace to sync </LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase Dynamic - (per file access)=20
  <UL>
    <LI>For each file or directory access through MVFS a check is made =
to locate=20
    disk location to re-direct IO,=20
    <LI>Directory version information built on the fly=20
    <LI>File access may involve a VOB cache in cleartext from source =
</LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase Snapshot - reload, rebase=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Compare View DB with VOB DB, according to config spec, transfer =
files to=20
    workspace as required </LI></UL></LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Developer Activities</H1>
<H4>Checkout, checkin, merge</H4>
<UL>
  <LI>Checkout=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Update repository DB to indicate checkout state, change file in=20
    workspace to writeable </LI></UL>
  <LI>Checkin=20
  <UL>
    <LI>For ClearCase, transfer file to VOB source and update DB with =
new=20
    version </LI></UL>
  <LI>Merge of file=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Compare of file in workspace with file transferred from =
repository with=20
    results to workspace </LI></UL></LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Commit change to project stream</H1>
<UL>
  <LI>Perforce - submit=20
  <UL>
    <LI>For files in changelist (add, ckout, delete), transfer files to =
depot=20
    and update depot files, update DB in such a fashion that a single DB =
write=20
    indicate operation complete=20
    <LI>File merges may be required to complete transfer from workspace =
to depot=20
    </LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase - deliver=20
  <UL>
    <LI>This a directory merge operation from change branch to =
integration=20
    branch=20
    <LI>For trivial case this is DB and and control communication =
between client=20
    and VOB server, no file transfer=20
    <LI>Non-trivial cases involve file or directory merges</C>=20
</LI></UL></LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Builds</H1>
<UL>
  <LI>Perforce=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Only Client workspace IO </LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase Dynamic=20
  <UL>
    <LI>MVFS based IO for each file=20
    <LI>Audited builds produce "Derived Object" recording each file =
version,=20
    addition control IO to View and VOB DB </LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase Snapshot=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Only View workspace IO </LI></UL></LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Labels</H1>
<UL>
  <LI>Perforce=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Specification based definition=20
    <LI>The actual label operation causes a DB update for each file =
version=20
    which is labeled </LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Control I/O as label applied to file or directory version=20
    <LI>Additional I/O to determine version if recursive or ConfigRec =
based=20
    label </LI></UL></LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Branches</H1>
<UL>
  <LI>Perforce=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Specification based=20
    <LI>Selection from branch selects from branch "depot", if modified,=20
    otherwise selection is by branch specification=20
    <LI>A submit to a branch, forces a DB branch update to the file if =
needed=20
    prior to the commit of the submit operation </LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Under control of local View config specification (or explicit =
command by=20
    file)=20
    <LI>Checkout causes branch of file prior to checkout activity=20
    <LI>branch is a DB update for file </LI></UL></LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Remote Development</H1>
<UL>
  <LI>Perforce Proxy=20
  <UL>
    <LI>File content is cached the 1st time referenced=20
    <LI>ALL control information is passed through to repository server=20
    <LI>Useful for decreasing file transfer IO from repository server =
</LI></UL>
  <LI>ClearCase MultiSite=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Maintains ReadOnly copy of files and DB for remote sites=20
    <LI>Synchronization between sites a separate managed process=20
    <LI>This site may only update information assigned to this site=20
    <LI>Extra merges may be required to integrate remote site changes=20
  </LI></UL></LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>In Summary</H1>
<UL>
  <LI>Develop a good model of what are components=20
  <LI>Research and understand the data transfer and processing =
activities=20
  <LI>Collect good performance measurements=20
  <LI>Identify bottlenecks=20
  <LI>Consider alternatives to address bottleneck=20
  <LI>Implement changes=20
  <LI>Repeat </LI></UL></DIV>
<DIV class=3Dslide>
<H1>Questions</H1>
<UL>
